WEBVTT

00:09:29.363 --> 00:09:32.797
AG: A more meaningful approach
is to focus on building a real connection.

00:09:32.821 --> 00:09:34.551
RH: The level up from that is,

00:09:34.575 --> 00:09:38.797
"Look, I like building up
alliances, friendships, relationships,"

00:09:38.821 --> 00:09:42.053
and, "Let's both invest
in a relationship."

00:09:42.077 --> 00:09:43.284
AG: At the highest level,

00:09:43.308 --> 00:09:46.403
the goal is to help people
because that's a value of yours,

00:09:46.427 --> 00:09:49.220
or because you believe in them
and their values.

00:09:49.244 --> 00:09:54.718
RH: The best is where, actually,
in fact, we share a mission in the world,

00:09:54.742 --> 00:09:58.576
and in that shared set of values,
we also have a friendship.

00:09:58.600 --> 00:10:01.003
AG: So, you know that to earn
that kind of respect,